  "description": [
    "Its A Real Comfort To buy a diamond in a store where you know there will be no misrepresentation If I tell you a stone is of a certain weight you know it is just that weight If I say it is a pure crystal white with out aflaw you kuow that is so My prices on gems this Spring are lower than ever I bought my stock before the recent 10 per cent advance F W BROMBERG 107 N 20th St IRON MARKET FIRM AT RECENTADVANCE CONTINUOUS BUYING OF BOTH SOUTHERN AND NORTHERN IRONSFOUNDRY AND SOFT GRADES WELL SOLD UP The Birmingham iron market continues firm at the recent advance to 10 for No 2 foundry Rogers Brown Cos Cincinnati cir cular of yesterdays date says There has been continuous buying of both northern and southern irons during the past week but the individual trans actions have not been of great magnitude The pipe companies and rolling mills seem to have purchased practically all the low grade southern iron in stock and that will be made for weeks to come Foundry and soft grades are fairly well sold up and there is no pressure on the market now from"
